<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>725</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén de ér nǚ yào yǒu xìn xīn de yǎn, shén de ér nǚ yào yǒu shùn fú de jiǎo.
 zǒu tiān lù yào yǒu jì tán hé zhàng péng, cái néng zǒu dào tiān jiā.
 jì tán shì dài zhe wǒ men de xīn xiàng zhe shén. zhàng péng shì yǐn wǒ men de jiǎo lí kāi shì jiè.
 gēn suí shén de rén bù néng méi yǒu jì tán. huí tiān jiā de rén bù néng bù zhù zhàng péng.
 zǒu a shén de ér nǚ men,
 wǒ men cóng yuǎn chù wàng jiàn nà róng měi de jiā xiāng. wǒ men shì shǔ shén de zi mín.</lyrics>
<title>shén de ér nǚ yào yǒu xìn xīn de yǎn 迦南725</title>
</song>